page-apps-dapp-description-cent: Social network a wunya sika denam NFT ahorow a wode bɛto gua so.
page-apps-dapp-description-decentraland: Boaboa, di virtual asase gua wɔ virtual wiase a wubetumi ahwehwɛ mu.
page-apps-dapp-description-ens: Edin a ɛyɛ mmerɛw sɛ wɔde bedi dwuma ma Ethereum address ne amansin mmeae mu.
page-apps-dapp-description-gitcoin: Nya crypto efri adwuma ye wɔ software a wɔabue ano so.
page-apps-dapp-description-gods-unchaine: Akwankyerɛ ɛfa aguadi kaad agodie. Nya kaad denam agodie a wubetumi atɔn wɔ asetra ankasa mu no so.
page-apps-dapp-description-augur: Fa kyakyatow to nea ebefi mu aba so. Di gua wɔ nsɛm ho gua ahorow so.
page-apps-subtitle: Hwehwɛ application ahorow a wɔakora so a ɛyɛ adwuma wɔ ethereum ne layer 2 ntwamutam so
page-apps-meta-title: Crypto dwumadie kɛse a ɛwɔ Ethereum so
page-apps-meta-description: Hwehwɛ crypto dwumadie wɔ ethereum: hwehwɛ DeFi, NFTs, Social, Gaming, Bridges, Privacy, Productivity & DAO dApps mu. Hwehwɛ onchain apps a wotumi de ho to so a wode bɛdi gua, anya sika, na woadi nkitaho.
page-apps-category-defi-description: DeFi yɛ amansin dwumadie kuw bi a ɛma wɔn a wɔde di dwuma no tumi bosea, bɔ bosea, di gua, na wonya mfɛntom wɔ wɔn crypto agyapade so.
page-apps-category-defi-meta-title: Ethereum DeFi dwumadie ahodoɔ — Ma bosea, Bɔ bosea na nya Mfasoɔ
page-apps-category-defi-meta-description: Hwehwɛ DeFi dwumadie kɛse wɔ Ethereum so ma boseama, boseabɔ, stablecoin a wɔde ma, boseabɔ ne on-chain DEX aguadi.
page-apps-category-collectibles-descript: Nneɛma a wɔboaboa ano yɛ ntanɛte so agyapade a ɛyɛ soronko na wontumi nsuasua.
page-apps-category-collectibles-meta-tit: NFT dwumadie a ɛyɛ sen na ɛwɔ ethereum so nyinaa din
page-apps-category-collectibles-meta-des: Hwehwɛ NFT dwumdie kɛse a wode tɔ nneɛma a wɔboaboa ano, di agoru ho nwoma, na wuhu ntanɛte agyapade foforo wɔ Ethereum gua ahorow a edi kan no nyinaa so.
page-apps-category-social-description: Asetenam yɛ dwumdie ahorow a wɔde ahyɛ aman nsa a ɛma wɔn a wɔde di dwuma no tumi ne afoforo di nkitaho na wɔkyɛ nneɛma a ɛwɔ mu.
page-apps-category-social-meta-title: Asetenam dwumadie wɔ ethereum so: farcaster, zora ne nea ɛkeka ho
page-apps-category-social-meta-descripti: Hwehwɛ nkrasɛm ne asetenam dwumadie a ɛyɛ papa paa wɔ ethereum so.
page-apps-category-gaming-description: Agodie yɛ dwumdie ahorow a wɔde ahyɛ obiara nsa a ɛma wɔn a wɔde di dwuma no tumi di agoru na wonya akatua.
page-apps-category-gaming-meta-title: Crypto ne NFT agodie ahorow a wɔahyehyɛ wɔ Ethereum so
page-apps-category-gaming-meta-descripti: Hu blockchain agodie a ɛyɛ sen biara a ɛyɛ anigye sɛ wobɛbɔ. MMORPG, kaad agodie, AI agodie, RPG, agodie a ɛnyɛ anibereɛ so
page-apps-category-bridge-description: Bridge yɛ amansin dwumadie ahodoɔ bi a ɛma wɔn a wɔde di dwuma no tumi de wɔn agyapadeɛ twene so wɔ network ahodoɔ ntam.
page-apps-category-bridge-meta-title: Ethereum bridge ahodo de ma network ahodo
page-apps-category-bridge-meta-descripti: Hunu crypto bridge papa aa wode betu wo gyapade afa layer ahodo ne networks ahodo so.
page-apps-category-productivity-descript: Dwumadie ye category wo decentralized applications so aa ema dwumadifo no ye dwuma yie.
page-apps-category-productivity-meta-tit: Dwumadie ne decentralized nipa hunu app ahodo
page-apps-category-productivity-meta-des:
Hwehwe Ethereum app de ma decentralized nipa hunu, nsie, DNS, ne sini komputing.
Fa akade aa yegye no di tu wo 'on-chain' dwumadie mu mpon.
page-apps-category-privacy-description: Nsie ye category wo decentralized applications so aa ema dwumadifo no tumi sie.
page-apps-category-privacy-meta-title: Ethereum nsie apps: tornado sika ne afoforo
page-apps-category-privacy-meta-descript: Hwehwe Ethereum nsie apps bi te se Tornado sika ne afoforo aa eboa ma wo sie, di nkitahodie aa obiara nhu, na etu 'on-chain' nsie mu mpon.
page-apps-category-dao-description: DAO ye kategori wo decentralized applications mu aa ema dwumadifo ho kwan ma omo bo decentralized nnwumakuo aa obiaa nhye omo so.
page-apps-category-dao-meta-title: DAO akade ahodo aa ewo Ethereum so
page-apps-category-dao-meta-description: Hunu DAO akade aa ewo soro wo Ethereum so de ma amamuo, sika siesie, abato, ne mafo nhyehye. Yi pu, manegye, na nyini wo decentralized dwumakuo no.
page-apps-suggest-an-app-description: Yɛrehwehwɛ dwumadie foforo a yɛde bɛka yɛn list ho bere nyinaa. Sɛ wunim dwumadie bi a wususuw sɛ ɛsɛ sɛ ɛwɔ list no mu a, yɛsrɛ wo ma yɛnhu.
page-apps-info-last-updated: Daa etwa so a woyɛ no foforo
